<HEADLINE> Nigerian War College Officers Start Tour of </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, March 23 (Xinhua) -- A team of Nigerian High
Ranking army officers from the Nigerian National War College led
by Ambassador Edward Martin has been here since last night for an
eight-day tour to study the defense situation of Tanzania.
</P>
<P>
