Defense Forces General Robert Mboma, Minister for Defense and
National Services Edgar Maokola Majogo and Speaker of the
National Assembly Pius Msekwa.
</P>
<P>
The delegation will also tour the Ministry of Foreign Affairs
and International Cooperation and the Planning Commission.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the delegation is expected to visit Arusha in
northern Tanzania on Thursday. 
</P>
