<HEADLINE> Ethiopia to Privatize Gold, Tantalum Producing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 24 (Xinhua) -- The Ethiopian Ministry of
Mines and Energy announced on Sunday that preparations have
already been completed to privatize the Legedembi gold and
tantalum producing plants in Adola Area, southern Sidamo Region.
</P>
