plot of 9.4 hectares, will be conducted in three phases within
five years including building of the Yangon World Trade Center,
the Yangon City Square and the Yangon Convention Center.
</P>
<P>
The new business district project is among the seven extended
by the Myanmar DHSHD, which include those of the Mingaladon
Industrial Park, the Thanlyin-Kyauktan Industrial Zone, the Sakura
Service Apartment, Shwe Hintha Inn, Mingalar Garden Hotel and Pan
Sea Hotel.  
