Turin in 35 minutes 11 seconds on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Over the last stretch of 12.333 kilometers race, Tergat fought
out a tight race with the favored Salah Hissou of Morocco who
finished in 35 minutes 20 seconds.
</P>
<P>
Kenya's Thomas Nyariki was third in 35 minutes 23 seconds.
</P>
<P>
