<HEADLINE> Sarajevo Festival Draws 1,200 Artists </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SARAJEVO, March 23 (Xinhua) -- The annual Sarajevo Winter
Festival has been participated by 1,200 artists from 30 countries,
local press reported on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The festival, which was held between February 7 and march 21,
featured 267 performances. During the period of the festival, it
was admitted to the European Association of Festivals.
</P>
<P>
Since 1984, Sarajevo has organized winter festivals annually,
even during the war years, drawing two million visitors and 11,000
artists from around the would. 
</P>
</TEXT>
